# [SECURITY-8] Credentials — Stored securely: Production credentials are set as Azure App
# Service environment variables (OS-level). This template shows the format; never commit
# real values. Double underscores (__) map to nested JSON config keys in .NET.
# For production deployment set these as environment variables in Azure.
# For local development, copy this file to backend/.env and fill real values.
ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection=Host=your-azure-db-host;Port=5432;Database=postgres;Username=your-username;Password=your-password;SSL Mode=Require;Trust Server Certificate=true
